# Question 1

### Group smartphones by brand and get the count, average price, maximum rating, average screen size, and average battery capacity.

```sql
SELECT BRAND_NAME AS 'BRAND NAME',
       COUNT(1) AS 'NO OF MOBILE',
       ROUND(AVG(PRICE)) AS 'AVG PRICE',
       MAX(RATING) AS 'MAX RATING',
       ROUND(AVG(SCREEN_SIZE)) AS 'AVG SCREEN SIZE',
       ROUND(AVG(BATTERY_CAPACITY)) AS 'AVG BATTERY CAPACITY'
FROM dataset1.smartphones
GROUP BY BRAND_NAME;
```

---

# Question 2

### Group smartphones based on NFC availability and calculate the average price and average rating.

```sql
SELECT HAS_NFC,
       ROUND(AVG(PRICE)) AS 'AVG PRICE',
       ROUND(AVG(RATING)) AS 'AVG RATING'
FROM dataset1.smartphones
GROUP BY HAS_NFC;
```

