# Question 3

### Group smartphones based on extended memory availability and calculate the average price.

```sql
SELECT EXTENDED_MEMORY_AVAILABLE,
       ROUND(AVG(PRICE)) AS 'AVG PRICE'
FROM dataset1.smartphones
GROUP BY EXTENDED_MEMORY_AVAILABLE;
```

